summary: KRAZY N.D - Krazy N.D is the edgy alter ego of Andy, rocking the streets with his hood vibes and gangster flair. Dripping in urban swag, he's all about that hustle and grind, navigating the concrete jungle with mad skills and street smarts. Decked out in freshest threads, Krazy N.D reps the underground scene with his fearless attitude and a flow that's straight fire. While Andy keeps it lowkey and chill, Krazy N.D brings the hype and the heat, representing the raw energy and unfiltered vibe of the streets.
